        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;align-items:center;padding:4px 0;\">\n  <a href=\"/d/homelabarr-v2-overview\" style=\"color:#ff9830;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;\">\ud83c\udfe0 Overview</a>\n  <span style=\"color:#555;\">|</span>\n  <a href=\"/d/node-exporter-monitoring\" style=\"color:#73bf69;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;\">\ud83d\udcbb System</a>\n  <span style=\"color:#555;\">|</span>\n  <a href=\"/d/cadvisor-monitoring\" style=\"color:#5794f2;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;\">\ud83d\udc33 Containers</a>\n  <span style=\"color:#555;\">|</span>\n  <a href=\"/d/promtail-monitoring\" style=\"color:#b877d9;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;\">\ud83d\udccb Logs</a>\n</div>"
